---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 文章
description: 4671 的个人博客文章归档。
nav: articles
permalink: articles.html
---
<main>
  <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="archive-title">
    <p>ARCHIVE</p>
    <h1 id="archive-title">文章</h1>
    <p>按时间保存写下的文字，也可以通过标签找到相近的内容。</p>
  </section>

  {% set posts = collections.posts %}
  <section class="listing" aria-label="全部文章">
    <header class="listing-header">
      <h2>全部文章</h2>
      <span>共 {{ posts.length }} 篇</span>
    </header>
    {% include "components/post-list.njk" %}
  </section>

  {% set allTags = collections.posts | getAllTags %}
  {% if allTags.length %}
    <section class="archive-tags" aria-labelledby="tags-title">
      <h2 id="tags-title">Tags</h2>
      <div class="tag-list">
        {% for tag in allTags %}
          <a href="{{ tag | tagUrl }}">#{{ tag }}</a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
  {% endif %}
</main>
